des:
Tickle your funny bone with a great dad joke. You can ask for a corny, one-liner, or pun dad joke. Or you can hear any of them by asking for a random dad joke.

You can unlock many more dad jokes by signing up to the Premium Subscription or by making a one-time purchase from the following dad jokes packs below:

Corny Dad Jokes Pack One
Pun Dad Jokes Pack One
One-Liner Dad Jokes Pack One

Get the latest updates and news on Great Dad Jokes by looking us up on Facebook. Just type in "Great Dad Jokes"
